<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:10:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧盟高级外交官博雷尔谈以色列、内塔尼亚胡和加沙战争：“以色列自卫的权利是有限度的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-to-self-defense-has-a-limit-top-eu-diplomat-on-netanyahu-settlers-gaza/00000191-9e18-d453-ab9f-fe9cfc570000</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔对欧盟在帮助加沙人民、建设中东和平以及遏制内塔尼亚胡政府中的极端分子方面做得不够感到沮丧。他在接受《国土报》采访时表示，“往好了说，我们是被动的，往坏了说是被动的，当然没有我们应有的积极主动性”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-to-self-defense-has-a-limit-top-eu-diplomat-on-netanyahu-settlers-gaza/00000191-9e18-d453-ab9f-fe9cfc570000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌曝光的针对以色列合作者的伊朗反情报行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/iranian-counter-intelligence-operation-targeting-israeli-collaborators-exposed-by-google/00000191-9f00-d453-ab9f-ff8cee220000</link><description>多年来，具有安全背景、讲阿拉伯语和波斯语的虚假职位列表一直在网上发布，显然是为了欺骗潜在的合作者；活动与 Shin Bet 透露的活动几乎相同</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/iranian-counter-intelligence-operation-targeting-israeli-collaborators-exposed-by-google/00000191-9f00-d453-ab9f-ff8cee220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高中工会因与财政部发生纠纷而宣布罢工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-school-union-announces-strike-amid-disputes-with-finance-ministry/00000191-9eb8-d172-abd9-febfaecc0000</link><description>以色列中学教师协会表示，财政部正在“不惜一切代价试图打破有组织的劳工，将教育系统私有化，并与教师签订个人合同，从而将他们变成合同工”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-school-union-announces-strike-amid-disputes-with-finance-ministry/00000191-9eb8-d172-abd9-febfaecc0000</guid></item><item><title>我为什么要离开以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-i-am-leaving-israel/00000191-9dc7-d314-a9f5-9df7403e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:29:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-i-am-leaving-israel/00000191-9dc7-d314-a9f5-9df7403e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 328 天：世卫组织官员称，以色列国防军同意暂停加沙脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-328-idf-agreed-to-gaza-pauses-for-polio-vaccination-who-official-says/00000191-9ec7-d453-ab9f-fecfd5d00000</link><description>获救的人质凯德·法尔汉·卡迪表示，以色列人质阿尔耶·扎尔马诺维奇在哈马斯囚禁期间因缺乏医疗救治而死亡。 美国、埃及和卡塔尔预计将在“几天内”提出新提案，以解决停战谈判中的两个关键问题 欧盟的外交政策酋长正式询问成员国是否要考虑制裁“一些以色列部长”煽动反巴勒斯坦行为 ■ 这是战争开始 328 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-328-idf-agreed-to-gaza-pauses-for-polio-vaccination-who-official-says/00000191-9ec7-d453-ab9f-fecfd5d00000</guid></item><item><title>2024 年巴黎残奥会：值得关注的以色列运动员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article-timeline/.premium/paris-2024-paralympics-the-israeli-athletes-to-look-out-for/00000191-9ed3-d314-a9f5-9ff3ca030000</link><description>以色列能否在 2020 年东京奥运会上夺得 9 枚奖牌？游泳、跆拳道、赛艇、网球和女子门球等项目的杰出选手很有可能在巴黎奥运会上取得好成绩</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article-timeline/.premium/paris-2024-paralympics-the-israeli-athletes-to-look-out-for/00000191-9ed3-d314-a9f5-9ff3ca030000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫市政府表示公共游泳池已关闭，为极端正统派开放，并实行性别隔离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</link><description>本月，一个市政游泳池在性别隔离的情况下悄然运营了几天，通过市政府的托拉文化部门提供打折门票，而市政府则隐瞒了该项目预算的详细信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-said-public-pool-was-closed-opened-it-for-ultra-orthodox-with-gender-segregation/00000191-9eb3-d453-ab9f-febf91990000</guid></item><item><title>“我希望有人付钱给我，我会和他住在一起，每个星期天我都会为他写弥撒。就是这样&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名年轻的以色列妇女与她的父亲一起飞往哥本哈根以获得外国公民身份，另一名妇女准备与她的双胞胎妹妹一起从军</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-29/ty-article/.highlight/i-want-someone-to-pay-me-ill-live-with-him-and-every-sunday-ill-write-a-mass-for-him/00000191-9ea1-d172-abd9-feb73a470000</guid></item><item><title>新报告称，到 2023 年，纽约 44% 的仇恨犯罪都是以犹太人为目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</link><description>纽约州审计长的一份新报告显示，纽约市所有重罪仇恨犯罪中有 65% 是针对犹太人的，而且越来越多的攻击针对的是人而不是财产</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/jews-were-target-of-44-percent-of-all-hate-crimes-in-new-york-in-2023-says-new-report/00000191-9e37-d18a-a1b7-bf378fed0000</guid></item><item><title>英国航空和伊比利亚快运周五恢复往返以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-iberia-express-resume-flights-to-from-israel-on-friday/00000191-9e51-d314-a9f5-9ff3bb320000</link><description>这些航空公司加入了法国航空、爱琴海航空公司和阿塞拜疆航空的行列，在以色列北部边境爆发冲突导致机场关闭后，这些航空公司于本周早些时候恢复了飞往以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:04:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-iberia-express-resume-flights-to-from-israel-on-friday/00000191-9e51-d314-a9f5-9ff3bb320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队加入辛贝特对约旦河西岸犹太恐怖主义的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-joins-shin-bet-warning-over-jewish-terrorism-in-west-bank/00000191-9e2f-d453-ab9f-feafbdcf0000</link><description>军方表示，约旦河西岸犹太人定居点的领导层几乎没有采取任何措施遏制暴力行为，辛贝特安全部门也表示，暴力行为“对以色列造成了难以形容的损害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-joins-shin-bet-warning-over-jewish-terrorism-in-west-bank/00000191-9e2f-d453-ab9f-feafbdcf0000</guid></item><item><title>政府宁愿忽视以色列经济的 5 个令人震惊的警告信号</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/5-alarming-warning-signs-for-israels-economy-that-the-government-is-ignoring/00000191-9e01-d824-abd7-feabf3f70000</link><description>过去几周的数据引发了人们对以色列经济未来的严重担忧。政府有行动的工具，却忙于内讧和挑衅</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/5-alarming-warning-signs-for-israels-economy-that-the-government-is-ignoring/00000191-9e01-d824-abd7-feabf3f70000</guid></item><item><title>拉皮德：内塔尼亚胡对十月前感到“无聊、漠不关心”。联合简报期间发出 7 项警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/lapid-netanyahu-was-bored-indifferent-to-pre-oct-7-warnings-during-joint-briefing/00000191-9da1-da8a-a991-bfe514450000</link><description>拉皮德在政府拒绝组建正式委员会后成立的民事调查小组作证说，内塔尼亚胡的高级军事助手表示，恐怖组织认为以色列的软弱是由于司法改革带来的社会动荡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:21:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/lapid-netanyahu-was-bored-indifferent-to-pre-oct-7-warnings-during-joint-briefing/00000191-9da1-da8a-a991-bfe514450000</guid></item><item><title>获救人质证实阿里·扎尔马诺维奇在加沙被关押期间被谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-says-arye-zalmanovich-was-murdered-in-captivity-while-held-together/00000191-9de8-d172-abd9-ffff6a8b0000</link><description>周三，凯德·法尔汉·卡迪从哈马斯的囚禁中被救出。他告诉在囚禁期间被谋杀的阿里耶·扎尔马诺维奇的儿子，他们在加沙建立了特殊的纽带</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-says-arye-zalmanovich-was-murdered-in-captivity-while-held-together/00000191-9de8-d172-abd9-ffff6a8b0000</guid></item><item><title>目击者称，蒙面以色列军队和警察袭击约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-army-and-police-forces-attack-palestinians-in-west-bank-eyewitnesses-say/00000191-9874-dd8c-addd-b9f4f7ca0000</link><description>一名目击者称，他们“戴着面具，穿着制服，但没有任何名牌或随身摄像机”。目击者补充说，部队指控这群人属于哈马斯，给其中一人戴上手铐，殴打他，并将他扔进河里；以色列国防军和边防警察表示现场没有部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-army-and-police-forces-attack-palestinians-in-west-bank-eyewitnesses-say/00000191-9874-dd8c-addd-b9f4f7ca0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷发现第一圣殿时期的古代印章，印有亚述恶魔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/ancient-seal-featuring-assyrian-demon-from-first-temple-period-discovered-in-jerusalem/00000191-9d73-d383-abb7-9d7f89cb0000</link><description>考古学家称，一块用古希伯来语刻有“LeYeho´ezer ben Hosh´ayahu”名字的黑石印章护身符显示了新亚述帝国对古代犹大国的文化影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/ancient-seal-featuring-assyrian-demon-from-first-temple-period-discovered-in-jerusalem/00000191-9d73-d383-abb7-9d7f89cb0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道伊朗准备对以色列进行报复袭击，美国加强了中东军事存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</link><description>尽管以色列本周挫败了真主党的袭击，但拜登政府正在加强其在该地区的空中和海上力量，同时向以色列紧急运送武器，因为人们越来越担心伊朗对德黑兰刺杀哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚进行报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 10:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队报告称，在正在进行的大规模行动中，五名西岸武装分子在清真寺内被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-killing-five-west-bank-militants-amid-ongoing-large-scale-operation/00000191-9d2f-dffe-a9b7-df3f5efb0000</link><description>军方称，遇难者中有一名伊斯兰圣战组织高级成员，他负责最近一次导致一名以色列平民死亡的袭击事件。巴勒斯坦卫生部报告自行动开始以来已有 12 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-killing-five-west-bank-militants-amid-ongoing-large-scale-operation/00000191-9d2f-dffe-a9b7-df3f5efb0000</guid></item><item><title>随着恐怖活动的加剧和以色列右翼的火上浇油，约旦河西岸正处于爆炸的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/with-terror-on-the-rise-and-israels-right-fanning-the-flames-the-west-bank-could-explode/00000191-9a88-d712-adff-bf9e84640000</link><description>更多的恐怖警告、极端主义定居者的袭击以及本-格维尔对阿克萨清真寺的挑衅正在使约旦河西岸达到沸点。 尽管以色列在营救一名以色列贝都因人质后加大了对哈马斯的军事压力，但辛瓦尔在谈判中仍然坚定不移</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 03:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">ht